<li class="projects"><a href="https://live-events.herokuapp.com/">Live Events</a></li>
<br>
<p>Live Events allows a user to see a list of events and where they are located with the Google Maps API. A user can then see who of their friends plan on attending each event. A user can achieve badges as the user becomes more active in the app. The app is built with Ruby on Rails using a PostgreSQL database. I used a Foundation and Sass front end with some JavaScript and AJAX functionality. Hosted the app on Heroku.</p>
<br>
<p>Unfortunately, I keep in touch with less than 1% of all my friends on Facebook. I want to be able to see a list of events, and whom of my friends plan to go to each event, so that I can choose whether to attend the event and have a real social interaction.</p>
