<li class="projects"><a href="https://season-survey.herokuapp.com/">Season Survey</a></li>
<br>
<p>Season Survey is a one-stop-shop for winter food, fun, and fashion. This Rails application was created using TDD, pair programming, and Git workflow. Season Survey employs AJAX to allow user voting, Action Mailer for email notifications, and CarrierWave for image uploads. As Bostonians who were worried about wicked winter weathah, we wanted a web application that would provide reviews of winter gear. To stay optimistic, we also offer reviews of winter fun and food.</p>
